    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and is a solid choice for anyone looking for a dependable vehicle without the premium price tag of a newer model. The exterior shows its age with some noticeable paint fading on the hood and roof, along with a few scuffs and minor dings around the body. Inside, the upholstery shows some wear and a few faint stains, but all features and electronics remain fully functional. Mechanically, it runs and drives well, though it will likely need new tires and a brake service in the coming months. It\u2019s a reliable workhorse that has plenty of life left for the right owner.",
