      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 12
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Presenting a truly collector-grade vehicle that stands in breathtaking, showroom condition. This car has been fastidiously maintained with an uncompromising attention to detail, having been exclusively garage-kept and shielded from the elements. The exterior paint retains a deep, mirror-like luster, free of chips or swirls, and is protected by a professional-grade ceramic coating. Inside, the cabin is immaculate; the premium leather remains supple with no visible wear or creasing, and the original scent persists. Every feature, from the advanced infotainment system to the climate control, functions exactly as it did the day it was delivered. Mechanically, the car is beyond reproach, boasting a full-service history at authorized dealerships and delivering a driving experience that is tight, responsive, and whisper-quiet. This is a rare opportunity for the discerning buyer to own a flawless example of automotive excellence.",
      "price": 48500.0,
